  "title": "Sales Manager (Medical Aesthetic Device)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Ready to lead </strong>and<strong> ignite growth </strong>in the <strong>fast-evolving world </strong>of <strong>medical aesthetics</strong>?</p><p><br /></p><p>We’re looking for a<strong> dynamic Sales to drive device and equipment sales, while expertly managing post-sales services that keep clients coming back.</strong></p><p><br /></p><p>In this role, you’ll craft standout sales strategies, build and empower a high-performance team, manage key accounts with finesse, and elevate our brand’s presence, all while ensuring clients stay radiant and loyal, fueling sustainable growth.</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Sales Strategy & Leadership:</strong><br />Develop and execute sales plans to meet/exceed individual and team target; lead and grow a high-performing sales team; track KPIs and performance metrics; improve underperforming territory.</li><li><strong>Team Development:</strong><br />Recruit, mentor, and manage sales talent; instil a results and customer driven culture; implement performance reviews and incentives.</li><li><strong>Service Sales Management:</strong><br />Oversee and promote value-added services such as clinical training, maintenance contracts, and post-sales support.</li><li><strong>Client & Key Account Management:</strong><br />Build strong client relationships, lead high-stakes negotiations, manage key accounts, and ensure customer satisfaction and retention.</li><li><strong>Market Strategy & Expansion:</strong><br />Identify new growth opportunities, collaborate with marketing, and stay informed on industry trends and competitor activity.</li><li><strong>Sales Operations & Reporting:</strong><br />Handle forecasting, budgeting, CRM optimization, and provide performance reports.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Bachelor’s in Business, Marketing, Life Science or related field.</li><li><strong>8 years in sales, with 5+ years in leadership roles</strong> within medical devices or aesthetics.</li><li>Proven success in <strong>exceeding revenue targets </strong>and l<strong>eading top-tier sales teams</strong>.</li><li><strong>Experience selling </strong>medical devices, equipment.</li><li><strong>Energetic, self-motivated, positive </strong>and <strong>goal-oriented.</strong></li><li>Strong <strong>negotiation, communication, and leadership skills</strong>.</li><li>Strategic<strong>, results-focused mindset</strong> with CRM and analytics proficiency.</li><li><strong>Deep understanding </strong>of the aesthetics/medical device market and its regulatory and distribution landscape.</li></ul>",
