    "description": "<p><strong>Servicom Medical</strong> <strong>– Singapore</strong> was set up in 1999. We have over 20 years of experience in business development, marketing, sales and engineering (after sales). We have the widest range of principals among the <strong>Servicom</strong> <strong>Medical companies</strong> – an indication of the company’s reputation and consistent customer satisfaction.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Here at <strong>Servicom Medical</strong>, we don’t just provide technology, medical and a<a href=\"https://servicomsingapore.com/about-servicom/\">esthetics equipment in Singapore</a> – we empower you with service. Clients who purchase <a href=\"https://servicomsingapore.com/about-servicom/\">medical equipment in Singapore</a> can trust us to provide assistance from the initial consultations to the after-sales support. Through <strong>Servicom Medical</strong>, you are given technology you can trust, use, and grow your business with.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Servicom Medical – Singapore</strong> is certified by <strong>Good Distribution Practice for Medical Devices (GDPMDS)</strong>. For more information, or to schedule a one-on-one appointment, contact us <a href=\"https://servicomsingapore.com/contact-us/\">here</a>.</p>",
